response.job_title: Chemical Engineer - Process optimization with programming emphasis - Jr. Developer
response.summary:
Chemical Engineer with experience in research, development and process automation using Python,  MySQL, SQL, and Visual Basic, among others. Professional expertise in research and development, optimization of sales logistics, achieving the creation of a database, tracking of ongoing projects and their management and consulting from different company departments.

Knowledge of tools such as Python, software development, Bash, SQL, MySQL, C++, Visual Basic, advanced excel, POO, database management and design (CRM), metabolic engineering, enzymatic and biochemical engineering, molecular thermodynamics, and computational quantum chemistry.
response.skills: Bash, Visual Basic for Applications (VBA), Ingeniería química, MySQL, Investigación de mercado, Investigación, Docencia, Metabolic Engineering, Matlab, LaTeX, Office 365, Visual Basic para aplicaciones (VBA), Python, Git, Github, C++, Aspen HYSYS, Power Apps, AutoCAD , Adobe Audition

Researcher, CTO and Co-founder of Muuds Colombia: StartUp dedicated to design (at the pharmacological level) and manufacture of Nicotine Salts, psychological support and e-commerce, as an effective method of cigarette replacement. 

Activities carried out in the company 
- Researcher in the manufacture and pharmacokinetic optimization of Nicotine salts 
- Developer of formulations for the product line 
- Designer of the production chain, quality control and production laboratory 
- Programmer of sales, inventory and product formulation CRM
- Co-designer of logistics in sales, Inbound marketing content 
- Co-designer of the psychological and pharmacological counseling program for cigarette replacement
